	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. in domino.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Non dubito, quin remiserit d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8418" cert="high">Myconius</persName> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1107" cert="high">Tridentinae</placeName> sessionis scripta.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Plures autem ego habeo epistolas, quas tu fortassis nondum vidisti, nempe <persName type="citizen_name">regis Galliae</persName> et <persName type="citizen_name">Anglię regis</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18520" cert="high">Ioachimi de Brandenburg</persName> et alia quędam a paucis visa; si non habes, significa.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p2916" cert="high">Schertlinus</persName> abiturus est fortassis die martis proxima; expectat equitatum, qui illum deducet in terram opimam episcoporum; nam digni sunt, tandem ut pereant, post tot homicidia cruentissima, quę perpetrarunt in pios Christi fideles martyres.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Fama fert cancellarium episcopi <persName ref="p7548" cert="high">Moguntini</persName> ab <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l213" cert="high">Hessis</placeName> captum, et si parum expectassent, cępissent episcopum, qui vix evasit a rustico admonitus.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Concilium <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1107" cert="high">Tridentinum</placeName> finem habet; evolant episcopi omnes nidos alios quaerentes tutiores.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l18" cert="high">Augustę</placeName> proclamatum buccina nullas nundinas <placeName ref="l157" cert="high">Francofordiae</placeName> fore.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Papa conqueritur <persName type="auto_name">Caesarem</persName> in Lutheranos esse mitem; se velle <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Gallo</placeName> adhęrere.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p18250" cert="high">Mauritius</persName> in armis est.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid putas futurum?</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vertetur brevi tota <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l822" cert="high">Germania</placeName> et digna, ut pereat, quę alias nationes perdidit devastavitque.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">D. <persName ref="p2916" cert="high">Schertlino</persName> venient brevi, hoc est 18. die huius mensis, 200 equites, quos vult ad defensionem contra hostes armatos habere, quo locum commodum exercitui paret.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quo autem tu putas <persName ref="p2916" cert="high">Schertlinum</persName> exercitum illum ducturum?</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Rustici <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2836">Sungavię</placeName> omnes die noctuque vigilant in sylvis, in oppidulis et in pagis; invitus est miles, qui mallet hostem quam amicos.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Onerantur variis rebus, ut ne seminare possint; exactio gravis imposita est a <persName ref="p18477" cert="high">Ferdinando</persName>.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2510" cert="high">Turcam</placeName> timent et nihilominus excitant isti homines varias tragędias.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basileę</placeName> 17. m[artii] 1552.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">T[uus] <persName ref="p1278" cert="high">Gastius</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Die Adresse ist fast ganz weggeschnitten.]</note>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">[...] lerten/... Hein/... lut/... rich/... her/... den.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
